flowchart TD
    A[Start: run reddit_pipeline.py] --> B[Load config.py<br/>GROUP_A: 12 terms · GROUP_B: 12 terms<br/>GROUP_C: 9 terms · date range · subreddits]
    B --> C{Select stream}
    C -->|Stream 1| D[Build anchor queries from GROUP_A<br/>12 queries × 3 subreddits<br/>LocalLLaMA · LocalLLM · SelfHosted]
    C -->|Stream 2| E[Build anchor queries from GROUP_B<br/>12 queries × 5 subreddits<br/>ChatGPT · OpenAI · ClaudeAI · LLM · Gemini]
    C -->|Both| F[Build anchor queries from GROUP_A + GROUP_B]
    D --> G[For each subreddit and anchor query]
    E --> G
    F --> G

    G --> H[PullPush search: submissions]
    G --> I[PullPush search: comments]

    H --> H1[Raw PullPush hits<br/>⚠ count not saved — logged only]
    I --> I1[Raw PullPush hits<br/>⚠ count not saved — logged only]

    H1 --> J[Apply GROUP_C filter on title + body]
    I1 --> K[Apply GROUP_C filter on comment body]

    J --> J1[Passed GROUP_C filter<br/>Stream 1: 321 submissions<br/>Stream 2: 839 submissions]
    K --> K1[Passed GROUP_C filter<br/>Stream 1: 594 comments<br/>Stream 2: 1 304 comments]

    J1 --> L[Map fields and assign stream label]
    K1 --> L

    L --> M[Deduplicate new rows by Reddit ID<br/>Stream 1: 915 unique records<br/>Stream 2: 2 143 unique records]
    M --> N[Load existing CSV outputs]
    N --> O[Merge existing + new by ID<br/>no overwrite]
    O --> P[Sort by date]

    P --> Q[Write reddit_submissions.csv]
    P --> R[Write reddit_comments.csv]
    P --> S[Write reddit_combined.csv]
    P --> T[Build/write stats.json<br/>by month, stream, label]
    T --> U[Step 2: run annotate_batch.py<br/>LLM annotation via OpenAI Batch API]

    U --> V{no_task_found?}
    V -->|False — tasks extracted| X[Annotated records with ≥1 task<br/>Stream 1: 207 records<br/>Stream 2: 773 records]
    V -->|True — excluded| Y[Excluded: no clear task found<br/>Stream 1: 708 records<br/>Stream 2: 1 370 records]
    X --> Z[Write reddit_annotated.csv<br/>Final annotated task dataset]
